  14:../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32l4xx_ll_bus.h ****       (+) This delay depends on the peripheral mapping.
